plan_decisions[1]{ts,author,decision,rationale,evidence}:
  "2026-07-22T04:42:59.148Z",codex-root,Add dedicated typed helpers for stable documented WebSocket commands while retaining ws call for integration-specific commands.,This preserves forward compatibility and improves validation and help for security-sensitive common workflows.,"Official WebSocket and authentication docs plus successful live get_panels, ping, expose_entity/list, and auth/sign_path calls."
plan_discoveries[1]{ts,author,text}:
  "2026-07-22T04:42:59.768Z",codex-root,"homeassistant/expose_entity/list can exceed large formatter limits on the live instance, so typed output should support filtering or summaries to remain agent-efficient."
